Feature: 
  As a user
  They can be able to share the search results easily.

Scenario: Sharing search results
    When a user wants to share the list of search results
    Then the user can click on the share results button and copy the URL and share it.

Scenario: Sharing specific repair business
    When a user wants to share the result of a sepecific repair business
    Then the user can click on the share results button on the pop up screen of the business
    And share the repair business.